<type>: <lowercase_summary>

# ⚠️ COMMIT RULES ENFORCED ⚠️
# 1. Start with one of these types:
#    note     : New technical notes or content
#    docs     : Changes to README, setup, or metadata
#    fix      : Correcting typos, broken links, or formatting
#    refactor : Reorganizing folders or splitting notes
#    asset    : Adding images, diagrams, or attachments
#    chore    : Maintenance (IDE config, .gitignore)
#
# 2. Use ONLY lowercase letters.
# 3. Keep the summary line under 50 characters.
# --------------------------------------------------
# Why is this change being made? (Optional body below)